Utterance.UttText: In bed 17 is Elijah Evett, 75 yrs old under Dr Gan came in with numbness of his feet.
And pain in his lower back.

Candidate.CandidatePreferred: Back structure, including back of neck

Utterance.UttText: He has been seen by the doctors today and he has been booked for ct spine, brain, thoracic tom.
Pain 6/10 on regular morphine and endone.
He is doubly incontinent of faeces and urine.
He is on IV therapy at 83 mls/hr.BGL of 5.5.
He is also for physio review.
They have not seen him yet.
And he is on normal diet.
He wears hearing aides on both ears.
